                                The most popular tool of online automation for testing on many platforms and browsers is Selenium, which supports rapid execution of continuous test cases and supports languages like Java, Python, and C#. Its benefits are that it makes for a faster test, reduces more manual intervention, and works with many browsers with an aim to ensure that the experience of the user remains seamless on any device.
