                            <div class="accordion-body accordion-bodyContent">
                                Open-source nature, multi-language support, and cross-browser compatibility are some of the reasons that make Selenium different from all other testing tools. QTP or TestComplete cannot support all browsers and platforms, but Selenium can test on varied platforms/browsers, making it unique and versatile. Features like Selenium’s rich support for CI/CD pipelines and scalability make it even more compelling to use at scale to automate web testing processes.
                            </div>
